      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 06:31:04 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67d7c1665b92e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67d7c164aef31.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67d7c16601413.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67d7c165f25b2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67d7c16642ccb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;The original author of the mod is SkalGate, Altros , Pig&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I only fixed the graphic bug of Link's face in the "Painting Rendering (World)" and "Painting Rendering (World and Link)" options, as well as added the "Black Link" and "White Link" options&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;To use the repaired "Paint Rendering (World)" option, select the "Paint Rendering (World) LoongLy" or "Paint Rendering (World) LoongLy2" option to use&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;To use the repaired 'Paint Rendering (World and Link)' option, select the 'Paint Rendering (World) LoongLy3' option to use&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Copy the decompressed file to the folder of [Your emulator installation path] \ WiIU Game \ Camu \ graphicPacks \ graphicPacks_CHS-V829 \ BreathOfTheWild \ Mods to complete the installation&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;mod原作者为SkalFate, Altros , Pig&lt;br&gt;本人仅修复了在“绘画渲染（世界）”和“绘画渲染（世界和林克）”选项中，林可脸部的图形bug，以及添加了“黑色林克”和“白色林克”选项&lt;br&gt;要使用修复过后的“绘画渲染（世界）”选项请选择““绘画渲染（世界）LoongLy”或者“绘画渲染（世界）LoongLy2”选项以使用&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="SelectedElement"&gt;要使用修复过后的“绘画渲染（世界和林克）”选项请选择““绘画渲染（世界）LoongLy3”选项以使用&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;将解压后的文件复制到【你的模拟器安装路径】\WiiU Game\Cemu\graphicPacks\graphicPacks_CHS_V829\BreathOfTheWild\Mods文件夹下即可完成安装</description>
